Package org.apache.drill.exec.expr.fn

Class FunctionAttributes

java.lang.Object
org.apache.drill.exec.expr.fn.FunctionAttributes
public class FunctionAttributes extends Object
Attributes of a function used in code generation and optimization. Represents the values contained in the annotations of a Drill function.
